content: Get ready, the legendary audiophile grade transport is running short to reach the Google Play very soon, the QUEEN is back!. `noozy` disappeared for quite some time and now she's back! Bringing her most sexy and stunning sound close to your ears. Along with its most well-known sound processing `Noozxoide Laboratories` technologies in the Android world, this time we introduce you the most complex sound design that would make your music sound tasty and delicious for all time.
New updated `Alchemy` allows to create desktop shortcut. Click on the icon to launch the application like it should be. `Alchemy` is a prototype version, the public release is ETA 2014.
Demonstrate the Project `EVAC` concept to investor, the barebone architecture and the client app that would making internet speed faster with peer to peer technologies.
Admiring my works? I demonstrate other projects that I worked on to investor, to see if they were showing any interested. They were amazed of what I did. Well, it's passion and love.

Been working on this project for two months. Drafting a test with Google Mirror API in a small hotel room. Glad the hotel has decent internet speed. Working on testing and evaluation `Google Glass` developer version. I am on Google Glass project.
Introducing to my new Android app, `CryoCELL`. A smart intelligent power management. The automatic profile knows when to fast or slow charging my phone without harming my device battery.

`EIZO-rewire PRO` series is getting more and more higher ranking these months in total 7th releases. This piece of high tech app turns every Android devices into a premium sound device, especially for audiophile lover. I also set up fans club at Google+.

Just finished having vidcon with my crews, we've been getting results from few countries that testing this newly design infrastructure for project `EVAC HyperDrive`. Average ping speed across many countries are 1-20ms, 20ms-50ms of pings. Download Speed avg 1Mbps-3Mbps, 10Mbps-40Mbps. Upload Speed avg 20-70Mbps. Some countries have lower than 10Mbps from the probe result that was probably due to ISP installed low quality cable or weather proof that affected the signal quality in the conductor is not properly well-planned.

`EVAC hyperdrive` the 10x blazing secured internet accelerator for Android. Delivers encrypted connection and boosting internet speed by using peer network, compressing and caching engine over remote server. Coming soon at Google Play ETA 2013.

Finally Out Now!! You can listen at SoundCloud and subscribe or search `DJ LOOUIS` for full length `DREAM TRAVEL` version. This is a fully remake version, I have modified a little bit to get more airy effects.
Setting up `Noozxoide Labs` community page at Google+. Instead, I hardly see pro audio users on Facebook. Google Plus is the ideal platform to set up for Noozxoide Labs fans.
